Rip notes: nothing was ripped

ECW: Hardcore Revolution features three all-new arenas that capture the intensity of ECW: The Madhouse Of
Extreme (NYC), The ECW Arena (Philly) and Pay-Per-View Events! You can also create your own Pay-Per-View
matches, wrestle the grueling ECW schedule in Career Mode, create your own wrestlers, and the freedom to
annihilate your opponents with weapons like ECW standby's: cheese graders and kendo-sticks, baseball bats, shovels, ladders and many more! Over 20 Game modes that push you to the EXTREME !!